1. Xinhua News Agency commented on the US "Genius Act": The credibility and international responsibility of the US dollar will affect global acceptance, and changing the form alone is not enough to consolidate the influence of the US dollar and stablecoins;
2. Jack Dorsey's company Block joined the S&P 500 index, and the company holds 8584 BTC;
3. Tether CEO: Will promote USDT compliance to enter the United States;
4. World Liberty Financial strategically purchased BANK worth about US$40,000 to support the development of the Lorenzo Protocol project;
5. Two newly created addresses withdrew 22,434 ETH from Kraken, worth about US$795 million;
6. The total market value of the giant whale AguilaTrades' holdings reached US$294 million, and the ETH short position made a large profit;
7. The giant whale made another move, adding nearly 4,800 ETH in 10 minutes;
8. 7743 BTC were transferred out from Coinbase, worth more than US$916 million;
9. The Bitcoin spot ETF had a total net inflow of $363 million yesterday, continuing its net inflow for 12 consecutive days;
10. The Ethereum spot ETF had a total net inflow of $402 million yesterday, continuing its net inflow for 11 consecutive days.
